data.whats-this#What's This?: Welcome to our API Documentation page! This API is designed to support the development of a mobile application that can classify various types of batik through the camera or user-uploaded images. :)
data.features#Features:
Our API offers the following key features:
Image Classification: Upload images or use the camera to classify and identify different batik patterns.
Detailed Information Retrieval: Access comprehensive information about each batik type, including its name, origin, history, and philosophy.
User-Friendly Integration: Easy to integrate with your mobile application, providing seamless functionality and user experience.
